item.title: CVE-2020-26207|2024-08-04T15:49:07.140Z -- martinjw -- dbschemareader
item.description: DatabaseSchemaViewer before version 2.7.4.3 is vulnerable to arbitrary code execution if a user is tricked into opening a specially crafted `.dbschema` file. The patch was released in v2.7.4.3. As a workaround, ensure `.dbschema` files from untrusted sources are not opened.
